exthheader.author: Ursula K. Le Guin; Ruth Robbins
exthheader.description: Ged is a peasant boy from Gont with a gift of magic. He goes to the School of Wizards on Roke Island. Attempting to prove his superiority with magic he recklessly brings forth a shadow being from the realm of the dead that he must confront.
exthheader.subject: Wizards
